data.description: Don't pass up this classic spacious New England Colonial with 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths. Located in the heart of Pittsfield within close proximity to Berkshire Health Systems, General Dynamics, public transportation and nearby Springside Park. Enjoy the traditional wrap around front porch or the back deck with a fenced yard.  A solid house that needs a little TLC and your personal touch to bring out it's character. There's a lot to offer with a 2011 heating system, a Bosch dishwasher and hardwood floors throughout.  Ample storage including full basement and walk-up attic.
